The paper focuses on exploring and exploiting the hidden resource in wireless channel capacity, which is a topic related to information theory (cs.IT) and networked systems (cs.NI). The paper also uses copula to represent the dependence structure of the underlying Markov process, which is a statistical method related to machine learning (cs.LG) and mathematical analysis (cs.MA).
